reviewText: I bought this blu ray to watch hot girls in 3D. What a waste of time. The film looks like it was shot in a hour. The girls had no direction at all, and looked bored out of their minds. Worst of all the girls with the exception of the girl on the blu ray case are not sexy or beautiful. None of the energy of the Girls Gone Wild films is in this film. It says in the credits that there was a director. Well the director failed! All you have are Girls in various poses who look as if they would rather be anywhere else. Even if it's just posing the director should have run through the scene before they filmed to make sure the girls would give it their all. I never thought I would see the day where I would say watching 6 bikini clad girls playing Twister on the beach would be boring, but it was. Even though the girls were not that hot, I would have liked it better if they didn't look so bored. I bought this on Ebay for $5.95 brand new. I went on Ebay yesterday and they are now selling it for $4.95! If that's not a tip off I don't know what is. Will you be disapointed if you buy this for $4.95? Not as much as you will if you pay $19.99!
